title: Trash Talk x Flatbush Zombies - "97.92" (OFFICIAL AUDIO STREAM)
description:
"97.92", from Trash Talk and Flatbush Zombies, is the second track off the forthcoming CONS EP VOL. 1. The track was recorded at Converse Rubber Tracks in Brooklyn, NY. The "CONS EP VOL. 1" compilation is scheduled to come out in early 2014.

Produced by: Garrett Stevenson of Trash Talk
Music by: Trash Talk
Lyrics by: Flatbush Zombies
Vocals by: Flatbush Zombies
